Palestinian patriot and polemicist, sets forth tonight on a journey
``In Search of Palestine.'' He carries a heavy load of memories of
a homeland that was taken by force, leaving many of its people in
refugee camps or under Israeli occupation. By Walter Goodman.
</P>
