   13. FALLING LEAVES, by Adeline Yen Mah. (Broadway, $13.)
</P>
<P>
   From a cruel childhood in China to life as a California
</P>
<P>
   physician: an autobiography.
</P>
<P>
   14. STILL ME, by Christopher Reeve. (Ballantine,
</P>
<P>
   $7.99.) The actor looks back at his life, especially
</P>
<P>
   the period since his crippling accident four years ago.
</P>
