<HEADLINE>
FROM M.D. TO I.P.O: CHASING VIRTUAL FORTUNES 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By SHERYL GAY STOLBERG   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
