<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-05 10:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3164 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-R-THISWEEK-REVIEW-2TA     07-05 0624
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-THISWEEK-REVIEW-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) 
 The Week in Review  
 (bl)  
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   New York Pauses for a Tall Tale
</P>
<P>
   On the last leg of what still seems a remarkable journey, Edwin
