<P>
   ARATON-COLUMN (Undated) _ A Sports of The Times column on this
summer of women in sports. By Harvey Araton.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS-ORIOLES (New York) _ Baltimore at the Yankees, 7:35
p.m. EDT start. By Murray Chass.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ALLSTARS (Undated) _ The American League all-star starters
named: Derek Jeter, the Yankee shortstop, is expected to be one of
them. By Murray Chass.
</P>
