   DRIVEBY-SHOOTER (Chicago) _ A criminal justice major named
Benjamin Smith returned to his old haunts over the Independence Day
weekend. According to the police and FBI, he fired one handgun and
then another at Jews, blacks and Asians. Now that young man is dead
at 21 _ his suicide ended his tear of violence. Those who
encountered Smith say they never saw him act violently before, but
they saw him progress from closet racist to active racist using an
assumed name, and then to public racist on the edge between
pamphleteering and violence. A profile by Bill Dedman. (Scheduled
to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.)
